[[span style="font-size:20px;font-family:'Courier Prime';color:black;"]]**Special Containment Procedures:** I’m only using the SCP document format so that this page blends in with the rest of the printing work. This document only exists to make a brief progress report - well, more like a goodbye. As far as I’m aware, they don’t sift through employee documents unless they’re uploaded to the database. Either way, even if they do, I’ve already finished my work. If your name is Hewlett, Kubitz, or O5-whatever, then it’s far too late for you to do anything. The end has been spelled out for you. Good luck.
